Class DalConnector

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, org.epics.css.dal.context.LinkListener, org.epics.css.dal.DynamicValueListener, org.epics.css.dal.ResponseListener
 class DalConnector
extends AbstractConnector
implements org.epics.css.dal.DynamicValueListener, org.epics.css.dal.context.LinkListener, org.epics.css.dal.ResponseListener

DAL Connectors are connected to the control system via the DAL API. All events received from DAL are forwarded to IProcessVariableValueListener큦 which abstract from DAL. For convinience the IProcessVariableValueListener큦 are only weakly referenced. The connector tracks for IProcessVariableValueListener큦 that have been garbage collected and removes those references from its internal list. This way IProcessVariableValueListener큦 must not be disposed explicitly.

Author:
Sven Wende
